<sect1 id="vision__kernels__bf16_8c_1autotoc_md85">
<title>CK-ENGINE KERNEL RULES:</title>
<para><orderedlist>
<listitem><para>NO malloc/free - memory via bump allocator, pointers passed in</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>NO OpenMP - parallelization at orchestrator/codegen layer</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>API must define: inputs, outputs, workspace, and memory layouts</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Pure computation - deterministic, no side effects</para>
</listitem></orderedlist>
</para>
<para>After changes: make test &amp;&amp; make llamacpp-parity-full </para>
</sect1>
